nhc_headline: ...GABRIELLE EXPECTED TO BE NEAR OR OVER THE AZORES AS A HURRICANE BY LATE THURSDAY OR EARLY FRIDAY...
summary: ...GABRIELLE EXPECTED TO BE NEAR OR OVER THE AZORES AS A HURRICANE BY LATE THURSDAY OR EARLY FRIDAY... As of 11:00 PM AST Tue Sep 23 the center of Gabrielle was located near 35.1, -54.3 with movement ENE at 22 mph. The minimum central pressure was 953 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 125 mph.
